 
View UML description

Each of the classes MainMenu, HelpPanel, GamePropertiesPanel, GamePanel, 
WinnerPanel, and TeamSelectionPanel extend the JPanel class. In addition, 
the GamePanel class will have functions to draw the current state of the
gameboard. The team selection panel has functions to create the selected 
teams and to update teams.

In the view class, it has functions to show each of the extended JPanel 
classes with actionListeners to display them at the appropriate time. The 
GamePanel and showTeamSelectionPanel 's have a keyListener so that they 
can recieve input from the user.